{"tid":392973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華人血統演員改洋姓打進荷李活","createTime":"2017-09-09T01:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T11:22:35.000Z","uid":66618,"like":13,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a6d7e2e44d5860a5e33f77b84b079d22a5d0d48","tid":392973,"uid":66618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T01:28:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170902/s00014/1504287215017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170902%2Fs00014%2F1504287215017&d=vAB8B4lwwixEeVJmoS8wNrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7e10f59b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170902%2Fs00014%2F1504287215017&h=0d8abeca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170902/s00014/1504287215017</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】美國影視界再惹種族歧視爭議，著名電視劇《神盾局特工》（Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.）的華裔混血演員汪可盈在社交網站批評荷李活種族歧視，自己要改掉華人姓氏才能打入這個圈子，希望盡力避免他人有同樣遭遇。<br />\n<br />\n被批隱瞞亞裔身分爭白人角色<br />\n<br />\n汪可盈周二在Twitter讚揚英國白人演員艾德史克林（Ed Skrein）辭演漫畫改編電影《天魔特攻》（Hellboy）日裔角色Ben Daimio的決定，為他挺身對抗荷李活常起用白人演員飾演亞裔角色的「洗白」現象致謝。有網民隨即質疑汪可盈將英文名字由Chloe Wang改成Chloe Bennet，亦是為了隱藏華裔身分、爭奪白人演員的角色。<br />\n<br />\n汪可盈其後回應說：「荷李活是種族主義的，只要我擁有一個令他們不快的姓氏，他們便不會錄用我。」她強調，改姓不會改變自己擁有一半華裔血統、在中國生活過等事實，但自己亦要「應付生活所需」。她將在自己擁有的平台上竭盡所能，確保沒有人再需要改名才能得到工作。<br />\n<br />\n在《神盾局特工》飾演白人黑客特工「震盪女」（Quake）的汪可盈父親為中國人，母親為美國人。去年她接受新聞網站The Daily Beast訪問時亦曾透露改名的經過，稱自己最初在荷李活處處碰壁，但改姓後首次試鏡便獲錄用，認為反映「荷李活的運作方式」。此後她成立組織，推動提升亞裔及太平洋島民在荷李活的代表性。<br />\n<br />\n（BBC/CNN）"},{"pid":"9eba8da6b9cb0ed57399235c5d562a5d6acd1786","tid":392973,"uid":35430,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T01:29:26.000Z","msg":"走啦屌你"},{"pid":"b52cc4d8d5b7bd6fda1d7d5e3c328592f0f5e9fb","tid":392973,"uid":35430,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T01:30:57.000Z","msg":"叫你老豆全家返大陸啦<br />\n到時你大把機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b548644cb8a071e5da0d846261597609a99997","tid":392973,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T01:31:27.000Z","msg":"中國強大了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8247c8b681f438b69a8dd82856b022e1a80994","tid":392973,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T01:51:34.000Z","msg":"估唔到震盪女都有主角做<br />\n<br />\nbtw依家先知佢混血同埋劇入面嘅能力"},{"pid":"13eccd1a11d2464ab9406c88e0687817ee9e90e3","tid":392973,"uid":130105,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T02:00:28.000Z","msg":"華人血統<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://esq.h-cdn.co/assets/cm/15/06/54d41358daa0d_-__im_1222w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fesq.h-cdn.co%2Fassets%2Fcm%2F15%2F06%2F54d41358daa0d_-__im_1222w.jpg&h=e68d3d13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79ae1d0ca87fea7509d8a0ed03118dcb51ae945a","tid":392973,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T02:01:30.000Z","msg":"正如我哋都唔會容許港獨份子進入行政立法機構，甚至好多企業都唔會容許港獨份子存在！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc8a8dc4ee95a68a4a21e98e9f3c1bb1c52267f","tid":392973,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T02:08:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>華人血統<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://esq.h-cdn.co/assets/cm/15/06/54d41358daa0d_-__im_1222w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fesq.h-cdn.co%2Fassets%2Fcm%2F15%2F06%2F54d41358daa0d_-__im_1222w.jpg&h=e68d3d13&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n混血成功"},{"pid":"bbea50ac8c732f12a8675af1e19d6b7cff1fc488","tid":392973,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T02:09:40.000Z","msg":"Stan Lee都係焗住改名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji